OL,5, A boy had a finger amputated after he  
OL,6, injured himself fleeing bullies at     
OL,7, school, his mother said.               
OL,9,FRaheem Bailey, 11, caught his finger   
OL,10,Fwhile climbing a fence to escape and   
OL,11,Fafter six hours of surgery, doctors    
OL,12,Fcould not save it.                     
OL,14,FHis mother, Shantal, said the pupil at 
OL,15,FAbertillery Learning Community was     
OL,16,Fsubjected to racist abuse, and bullying
OL,17,Fbecause he is small for his age.       
OL,19,FGwent Police and Blaenau Gwent council 
OL,20,Fare investigating what happened.       
